    <h1 class="heads text-center">AWARD WINNING AGENCY</h1>
    <p class="para text-center">In 2003 Meet the Danes received a Danish award called the Initiative Award from “Fonden for Turismens Fællesråd”.In 2002 Meet the Danes received a prestigious International tourism award (British Guild of Travel Writers’ Silver Otter Award) for “BEST OVERSEAS TOURISM PROJECT”. An award we of course were very happy and proud to recieve. This recognition, which has been featured in media worldwide, has further increased the interest in our Meet the Danes events.
    </p>
    <h6 class="heads-sm text-center">COME MEET THE DANES</h6>
    <br>
    <p class="para text-center">Many nationalities visit Denmark every year. To give our foreign guests a different and more personal experience of Denmark and Danes, Meet the Danes invites them to visit the Danes at their private homes. Here, the guests join the Danes in a homemade dinner and the guests experience the Danes and the Danish culture and lifestyle. Thousands of guests have visited our hosting families, and got a very personal experience of Denmark, and the Danes. During these dinners many of our hosts and guests form new friendships, and some hosts have been invited to visit their guests in their home country.
    </p>
